snippet.title: Holistic Health Studies—SFSU
snippet.description: The Institute for Holistic Health Studies (IHHS) is dedicated to providing San Francisco State University and the broader community with a deeper understanding of health and healing from a holistic perspective, integrating interdisciplinary ideas and practices from around the world. IHHS is committed to excellence in teaching, research, and service, and to the dissemination of innovative health promotion curricula in higher education. For more information, visit: https://www.sfsu.edu/~ihhs/
